text: Julienne Boudewijns (born 11 August 1929) is a Belgian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belgium Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Antwerp
